- Knowledge of TDD principles;
- Knowledge of publishing applications in the App store;
- Knowledge of dependency management (SPM/CocoaPods);
- Fluency in English;
- Living in Lisbon, Braga or Coimbra (hybrid role).

Offer:
- Empowering Work Culture: Immerse yourself in a supportive, safe, and respectful work environment where every voice matters;
